And here I am.

45
00:05:39,389 --> 00:05:40,465
Uh.

46
00:05:46,375 --> 00:05:48,932
You must excuse my appearance.

47
00:05:49,098 --> 00:05:53,411
We need to get you
some medical attention.

48
00:05:53,536 --> 00:05:56,231
Please... allow me to escort you.

49
00:05:58,357 --> 00:06:05,615
Ah, you... you won't
need this anymore.

50
00:06:07,575 --> 00:06:10,495
Your ordeal is over.

51
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:31,680
My deepest condolences
on your loss, Mrs. Bell.

52
00:06:31,805 --> 00:06:32,934
Thank you.

53
00:06:34,441 --> 00:06:36,017
How in God's name

54
00:06:36,142 --> 00:06:38,553
did you make your way back here?

55
00:06:38,678 --> 00:06:43,824
Uh... can't remember his name, um...

56
00:06:43,949 --> 00:06:47,027
A Southerner, I think.

57
00:06:47,152 --> 00:06:48,395
Bohannon?

58
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:52,323
Yes, I believe so.

59
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:55,790
Hmm.

60
00:07:09,303 --> 00:07:11,150
Did I tell ya about me rendez-vous

61
